title: Nelsão
text: Nelsão, also known as Estádio Nélson Peixoto Feijó is a multi-use <a href="stadium">stadium</a> located in <a href="Macei%C3%B3">Maceió</a>, <a href="Brazil">Brazil</a>. It is used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and hosts the home matches of <a href="Sport%20Club%20Corinthians%20Alagoano">Sport Club Corinthians Alagoano</a>. The stadium has a maximum capacity of 10,000 people.
